parameters.name: START TIME
parameters.description:
Spacecraft event time (UT) at which the particle counting begins.       
      Time is given in the format of `yyyy-mm-dd hh:mm:ss.sss'.

parameters.name: MOTOR_MOVEMENT
parameters.description:
LECP motor movement flag (0 = no movement; 1 = movement during          
      accumulation.

parameters.name: PL01_RATE
parameters.description:
Counts per accumulation measured in energy channel PL01                 
      (24-48 keV/nuc. protons and ions).

parameters.name: PL02_RATE
parameters.description:
Counts per accumulation measured in energy channel PL02                 
      (48-80 keV/nuc. protons and ions).

parameters.name: PL03_RATE
parameters.description:
Counts per accumulation measured in energy channel PL03                 
      (80-137 keV/nuc. protons and ions).

parameters.name: EB04_RATE
parameters.description:
Counts per accumulation measured in energy channel EB04                 
      (112-183 keV/nuc. electrons).

parameters.name: EBP04_RATE
parameters.description:
Counts per accumulation measured in energy channel EBP04                
      (112-183 keV/nuc. electrons).
